<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WebApp Email Verification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Hi {{ name }}</p>
    <p>Please verify your email address by clicking the link below:</p>
    <p><a href="{{ verificationLink }}" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none;">Verify Email</a></p>
    <p>If you did not create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
</body>
